	"grade.clean_shift": [
		"[font_size=18][color=#2ecc71][b]Clean shift.[/b][/color][/font_size]\nThe physical load matches the digital AS400 twin. The truck is sequenced correctly for the store — C&C nearest the doors, Service Center deepest. Every promise date was respected, every committed item is on board. The store's receiving team will unload this truck in the order they need, with a confirmed digital record to match. No calls back to Tilburg, no missing items, no customer waiting at an empty counter.\n\n",
