	"grade.conditions_pressure": [
		"[color=#c0c8d0]Late-arriving pallets added pressure during this shift. Rework and prioritisation decisions are harder when the truck is filling up and new pallets keep arriving. These are the moments where preparation — checking the RAQ early, leaving space for possible arrivals — makes the difference.[/color]\n\n",
		"", "", "", "", "", "", "",
	],
	"grade.conditions_raq_miss": [
		"[color=#c0c8d0]The RAQ was not checked before loading began. Missing items — C&C pallets, transit rack collis — are visible in the RAQ before the first pallet is scanned. Checking it costs nothing before Start Loading and can prevent most of the issues above.[/color]\n\n",
